{"type": "article", "id": 56613, "title": "可重复使用的吸管，分拆后清洗也变得更容易｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-20T22:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 26110, "name": "Stellar Works"}, {"id": 809, "name": "Vitra"}, {"id": 52677, "name": "Charles & Ray Eames"}, {"id": 52914, "name": "Natchar Sawatdichai"}, {"id": 28105, "name": "Philippe Malouin"}, {"id": 52915, "name": "Chu Hiu Ching"}, {"id": 52916, "name": "Cheung Wa"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 181, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180920200156pMscV5nlZ0LHNS6u.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #48494d; -webkit-text-stroke: #48494d} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 16.2px Times; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 19.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #48494d; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #48494d} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #48494d; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #48494d} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Icicle Straw by Chu Hiu Ching &amp; Cheung Wa</h3><p>Icicle Straw 是 2018 亚洲设计奖的获奖作品，操刀设计的是韩国设计师 Chu Hiu Ching 和 Cheung Wa。</p><p>用仅仅 10 分钟去满足口腹之欲后丢弃的一次性吸管，却要用上很久很久时间才能完全分解。一次性的吸管瞬间变成垃圾，除了送到堆填区，亦有可能流入海洋对生态环境造成破坏，甚至进入食物链，影响人类的健康。</p><p>Icicle Straw 的概念不只是一支环保可重复使用的吸管。它简易的组合及分拆方式，不但令清洗更容易，更卫生，亦让它使用起来更接近我们日常使用的餐具。设计师希望能够鼓励人们都是用可重复使用的餐具，减少地球废物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200233pCgEjRu9wfXFIrMD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200232vEdXFs6TrJMQ7VZp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200229PrTJypOCgnbIN8ck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200233Aex4bwLERHicmBMv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200230vwndXEU8cozK1mJy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/09/19/a-fish-friendly-straw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Offset Table by Philippe Malouin</h3><p>英国设计师 Philippe Malouin 今年收获了 Wallpaper* 杂志评选的“年度设计师”荣誉。在今年的伦敦设计节上，Philippe Malouin 展示了其为新西兰家居品牌 Resident 设计的一张桌子 Offset，采用坚固的橡木制作而成，亮点在于桌腿是通过偏心螺纹连接到桌面部分。</p><p>整张桌子没有用到任何支架或金属嵌件元素，仅靠材料自身的重量保持其稳定性。按照 Philippe Malouin 的说法，他习惯于将产品以尽可能简单的形式呈现出来，一旦规划出产品的基本形状，就需要给设计做减法，去掉尽可能多的冗杂元素，正如这张桌子所呈现的一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200312bP6dsvQ3lxuY9gI0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200313DYJbQFLiSWe92yPo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200313kSj3No5E4PZ8YpXu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200313rzCwePpXDZlvWf7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200314QRb1ZeDlpBGaO8q5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200314Hwi7U9tbcRDCPvTX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.095355\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200314obcEVWLiJwdtmZPx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/offset-dining-table-philippe-malouin-solid-oak-resident-09-20-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Paper Blind by Natchar Sawatdichai</h3><p>为了避免浪费资源，目前在伦敦工作的泰国设计师 Natchar Sawatdichai 以纸张等可持续性的材质，开始设计生产家用物品。比如这款纸质百叶窗，一共包含了三个元素：百叶窗本身、悬吊用的绳子、固定高度用的滑轮。Sawatdichai 将纸张切割、折叠成立体的图案。</p><p>负责调整百叶窗高度的绳子和滑轮，就位于百叶窗的中央，如果想要替换窗帘，只要将窗帘从支架中滑出，换上新的窗帘就行了，更换后，使用者还能自行裁剪百叶窗的两侧，让百叶窗缩小到想要的尺寸，或是符合支架的尺寸，如果看腻了百叶窗原本的形状，也能透过调整绳子和滑轮，调整百叶窗的形状，可说是能够因应使用者各种需求的个性化百叶窗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t0711krhqbv\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200456V1xEbZpomg8iBnk5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497778\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200456yYpLcZxI0GNSXi5q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200457SlzUcIBpMeh30nyu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018092020045767CuslFmZJAbPWyj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200457pVCGukA9cMDFaLmd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200457qLQloFgZbW3JemNS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/natchar-sawatdichai-paper-blinds-09-19-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Eames Radio by Charles &amp; Ray Eames for Vitra</h3><p>瑞士设计品牌 Vitra 与设计史上的传奇夫妇 Charles &amp; Ray Eames 一直保持着紧密的合作关系，他们合力缔造了一系列经典设计。包括一款造型紧凑的小收音机，不过早在 1950 年代早期便已停产。</p><p>今年秋天，Vitra 决定重新推出 Charles &amp; Ray Eames 夫妇的这款代表作 Eames Radio，采用优雅的胡桃木作为外壳，配备英国制造商 REVO 的最新技术，限量发售 999 台，售价 999 美元，<a href=\"https://www.vitra.com/en-us/product/eames-radio\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200604nm1KLcyPBrdHRWtI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200605Vs5FR1BXCwxIY9Og.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200605Zw5cFWivJNxQf7IU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200606XvpJ2u14SFElIjzV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497555\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Louisiana Collection by Stellar Works</h3><p>家居设计品牌 Stellar Works 最近重新推出了三件 1950 年的中古家具，原作出自丹麦建筑师 Vilhelm Wohlert 之手，以庆祝路易斯安那现代艺术博物馆成立 60 周年。</p><p>Louisiana 系列包括两把椅子和一盏灯，原是 Vilhelm Wohlert 为 1958 年开幕的博物馆而设计，另有一把酒吧椅子当时也推出了原型制作，但从未进行过商业化量产。</p><p>座椅采用弧形靠背和带衬垫的圆形座椅，呼应博物馆的建筑样式；吊灯的设计灵感，则是源自哥本哈根皇家艺术学院的一盏酒等，半球状的铜质吊灯，复古味儿十足。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200658YkCjTohlpag7AQ4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665821\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809202006593TBNHCeoA6sPylEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200700SNFxvHB2LKrMecf1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180920200701dUkHGVhf8Dv4POAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/09/20/louisiana-museum-stellar-works-mid-century-furniture-vilhelm-wohlert/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}